platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Peacock TV is for serious TV fans. It has plenty of familiar titles: The Office, 30 Rock, Parks and Recreation, Saturday Night Live, Downton Abbey, Two and a Half Men, Yellowstone, The King of Queens, and Law & Order: SVU, to name a few. Youll also find new episodes of The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon and kids shows like Curious George, as well as live coverage of Premier League soccer. Looking for wrestling? Peacock is now the home of the WWEs new events and its giant streaming library.
